# 4D Persona Implementation Context

**Project**: Soccer-AI
**Completed**: 2025-12-31
**Status**: PRODUCTION READY

---

## Implementation Summary

The 4D Persona Architecture transforms Robert from a "costume" (declared personality) into a "computed position" - a dynamic persona whose state is mathematically derived from live data.

### The Formula: P(t) = (X, Y, Z, T)

| Dimension | Name | Source | Example |
|-----------|------|--------|---------|
| X | Emotional | Match results API / DB | WWDLW → confident |
| Y | Relational | Unified KG edges | "Liverpool" → rivalry mode |
| Z | Linguistic | config.py regions | Man Utd → Mancunian |
| T | Temporal | Conversation history | Turn 5 → rising |

