## Frontend 4D Indicator

The Flask frontend displays a 4D position indicator:

```html
<div class="position-4d">
  <div class="axis-indicator" id="axis-x">
    <span class="axis-label">X</span>
    <span class="axis-value">😊 confident</span>
  </div>
  <div class="axis-indicator" id="axis-y">
    <span class="axis-label">Y</span>
    <span class="axis-value">⚔️ Liverpool</span>
  </div>
  <div class="axis-indicator" id="axis-z">
    <span class="axis-label">Z</span>
    <span class="axis-value">🔵 mancunian</span>
  </div>
  <div class="axis-indicator" id="axis-t">
    <span class="axis-label">T</span>
    <span class="axis-value">📈 turn 3</span>
  </div>
</div>
```

